name: 2022 Commonwealth Avenue, Brighton, MA 02135, USA
directions: The key is hanging on a hook inside the left half of the building. The store, not the garage. Right when you walk in, on pegs to the right by the door to the garage. You can just grab the key, its attached to a snow scraper. Its sometimes high up, so you might have to ask the employee by the counter to grab it for you. Neither of us will give you any trouble.
comment: I'm non-binary (they/them), and I currently work here. If I'm working yay, if not, my coworker or anyone else won't have an issue with you grabbing the key. The restroom is on the left side of the building, behind the dumpster. Put the key in the top lock, and turn it to the right to unlock it. After, turn it to the left to lock it again, and drop the key off!
